      <p>po rozpoznaniu w dniu 10 lutego 2000 roku</p>
      <p>z wniosku <span class="anon-block">A. S.</span>, <span class="anon-block">ur. (...)</span>w <span class="anon-block">W.</span>, syna <span class="anon-block">P.</span>i <span class="anon-block">E.</span>
